 /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講解下fmcg mkt要做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fadcd953fc67cb590d7e746dc6ee8a99aaea7f","tid":47623,"uid":67234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4cacd8e1862a076f5201f939f1d8b359e7c5125d","tid":47623,"uid":70857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T18:53:33.000Z","msg":"想做event 類似大公司既marketing communication team 好冇做?"},{"pid":"ccfd75653afe8648a01bc0164cdf502ea8c122da","tid":47623,"uid":26542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩10點收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講解下fmcg mkt要做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常有2種<br />\n有d公司入面會分brand team 同 trade mkt<br />\nBrand team 做ATL<br />\nTrade mkt 做 BTL<br />\n<br />\n有d公司得1條Mkt team , 做晒ATL + BTL"},{"pid":"0eb6bb39246222eb57138a10e6be3dc7ddf9e192","tid":47623,"uid":19265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講解下fmcg mkt要做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常有2種<br />\n有d公司入面會分brand team 同 trade mkt<br />\nBrand team 做ATL<br />\nTrade mkt 做 BTL<br />\n<br />\n有d公司得1條Mkt team , 做晒ATL + BTL</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做晒真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec15b5e88da565df458ec9980a3a887f2f4386aa","tid":47623,"uid":19265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8-9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩10點收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔自爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b9303e655221d5798a443667c0040893a65a6d","tid":47623,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"此post 浮返上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20e4307bd1545ee9ffcafc4fc854468eda5d3e0","tid":47623,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"大公司先有正常既 Marketing Team，唔同 industry 會有小小分別，但通常係 Brand Marketing, Product Marketing。上面既巴絲講既 Event Marketing 理論上都係呢兩種。而理論上有 D 會再拆理，尤其是後者有部份會分埋唔同 Product 既 Acquistion 同 Retention。不過濕鳩細公司 Marketing = Sale <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n唔好諗到 Marketing 等於諗下橋好得意，基本上係跟公司方向，做下濕鳩野又一日，部份 Industry 會接觸多 D Consulting Company、Production House 之類。<br />\n我做個邊用左年幾兩年攪個 Global Homepage Redesign，Internal Testing 完出街唔夠一年就收到一份由 CEO 同其他高層傳過來既文件，原來佢地屎忽鬼搵左間英國 Consulting Firm 比意見做 Rebanding，問我地意見。心諗整完樣野無耐你突然間又玩既既野，唔單止個 Homepage 可能要再攪過，什至成個機構既 Template、Tag Line 同 Giveaways 又要再做過，一重整又 N 咁多意見，鬼佬又屎忽鬼遲覆你，到話真正推又話邊樣唔好，班 Country 什至乎 Regional Director 又要加巴嘴懶有見地咁，勁想屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"af28096d31973ba3d65548bcba79c56afc60f861","tid":47623,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T22:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大公司先有正常既 Marketing Team，唔同 industry 會有小小分別，但通常係 Brand Marketing, Product Marketing。上面既巴絲講既 Event Marketing 理論上都係呢兩種。而理論上有 D 會再拆理，尤其是後者有部份會分埋唔同 Product 既 Acquistion 同 Retention。不過濕鳩細公司 Marketing = Sale <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n唔好諗到 Marketing 等於諗下橋好得意，基本上係跟公司方向，做下濕鳩野又一日，部份 Industry 會接觸多 D Consulting Company、Production House 之類。<br />\n我做個邊用左年幾兩年攪個 Global Homepage Redesign，Internal Testing 完出街唔夠一年就收到一份由 CEO 同其他高層傳過來既文件，原來佢地屎忽鬼搵左間英國 Consulting Firm 比意見做 Rebanding，問我地意見。心諗整完樣野無耐你突然間又玩既既野，唔單止個 Homepage 可能要再攪過，什至成個機構既 Template、Tag Line 同 Giveaways 又要再做過，一重整又 N 咁多意見，鬼佬又屎忽鬼遲覆你，到話真正推又話邊樣唔好，班 Country 什至乎 Regional Director 又要加巴嘴懶有見地咁，勁想屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n見人講marketing = sales真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33cef06de6b03c6a50dd4c7c47b7868d33b1044","tid":47623,"uid":68897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T22:37:46.000Z","msg":"喺某間fmcg做過intern，唔明點解mkt team好似好少人個個忙到隻狗咁...<br />\n<br />\n有條友last day走埋黎同我講千祈唔好入行、職已辭、做五年都唔過20k之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b96f93911840b58c6be5287b77738e69f02ed2","tid":47623,"uid":26542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺某間fmcg做過intern，唔明點解mkt team好似好少人個個忙到隻狗咁...<br />\n<br />\n有條友last day走埋黎同我講千祈唔好入行、職已辭、做五年都唔過20k之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFMCG 人工唔差架wo<br />\n但忙到隻狗咁就真既"},{"pid":"93648be04d3e084990b0ed6638aaa01d7a759c6a","tid":47623,"uid":27285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"做緊酒店marcom+PR+digital marketing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜都掂下咁"},{"pid":"188890f0353c413e955910ad8c93878fd33475e4","tid":47623,"uid":70857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"做events and communication 係咪好chur 睇見好似幾好玩"},{"pid":"02fd01790b8b5f69a24daa0ec0443b48bb28f1f8","tid":47623,"uid":9032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做events and communication 係咪好chur 睇見好似幾好玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做緊marcom<br />\n當啲events好密<br />\n呢個event仲準備緊<br />\n又嚟下一個新event要準備<br />\n就唔係太好玩嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過做完之後會好開心有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080a0c4a2c79322a08742c35841c8a726b4844fc","tid":47623,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"Digital marketing 準備考政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9155746171307b686a32cc1ab458ecb35ab8940f","tid":47623,"uid":5662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Digital marketing 準備考政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4996a1f41d6671b025952c00e20d4c1ea2323e","tid":47623,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike"